\cb3 Not only is your idea compatible, but Flow-Based Programming (FBP) is arguably the most natural home for a codec piping system. By moving from a linear pipeline (A \uc0\u8594  B \u8594  C) to a Graph Architecture, you are upgrading from a "garden hose" to a "smart grid."\cb1 \
