\cb3 In the world of FBP and Agentic Networks, the most relevant DSLs fall into three categories:\cb1 \
\
\cb3 1. The Industry Standard: Flow-Based Programming (FBP) DSL\cb1 \
\cb3 There is a literal language called .fbp (used by frameworks like NoFlo). It is designed to be human-readable and describes exactly what you want: nodes and the pipes between them.\cb1 \
