\cb3 Cons: Requires a specific parser to turn this text into JavaScript objects.\cb1 \
\
\cb3 2. The "Agentic" JSON-DSL (Recommended)\cb1 \
\cb3 Since your backend is Node.js and your frontend is a web dashboard, using a JSON-based DSL is the most practical choice. It allows you to "ship" the logic from the Mac Mini to the browser so the dashboard can draw the graph automatically.\cb1 \
