\cb3     \{ "from": "n2:out", "to": "n3:in" \}\cb1 \
\cb3   ]\cb1 \
\cb3 \}\cb1 \
\cb3 Pros: Native to JavaScript; easy to save in a database; easy to visualize with libraries like D3.js or React Flow.\cb1 \
